rl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Believes%20In%20Rule%20by%20Chaos%20in%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20high%20time%20we%20started%20asking%20about%20the%20complicity%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20which%20has%20devastated%20Manipur.%20And%20hold%20the%20prime%20minister%20responsible%20for%20it.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20said%20that%20by%20remaining%20proactively%20%E2%80%98inactive%E2%80%99%20in%20Manipur%2C%20it%20has%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20a%20long%20lasting%2C%20if%20not%20permanent%20division%20in%20the%20entire%20North%20Eastern%20region.%20It%20is%20no%20mean%20achievement%20for%20a%20party%20which%20rules%20by%20creating%20more%20and%20more%20division%20and%20chaos%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20inconceivable%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20has%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdilution-of-article-370-brought-unprecedented-progress-and-security-to-jk-centre-tells-sc%5C%22%3Eability%20to%20silence%20all%20voices%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20proactively%20intervenes%20through%20its%20agencies%20in%20West%20Bengal%20or%20other%20states%2C%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20despite%20saying%20it%20wants%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20commentariat%20and%20the%20opposition%20too%20has%20been%20treating%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20as%20an%20act%20of%20callous%20indifference%20on%20its%20part.%20The%20blame%20is%20being%20put%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-video-tarnished-states-image-says-cm-biren-calls-for-statewide-protests%5C%22%3EBiren%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rightly%20so.%20But%20how%20do%20we%20explain%20the%20failure%20of%20a%20Union%20government%20headed%20by%20a%20man%20who%20keeps%20asking%20the%20people%20across%20India%20to%20give%20power%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20states%20too%20so%20that%20he%20can%20directly%20control%20their%20affairs%20at%20the%20state-level%20too%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20say%20that%20it%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20contain%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20an%20unprecedented%20number%20of%20central%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20extraordinary%20power%20that%20it%20has%20assumed%20by%20sending%20its%20special%20representative%20to%20%E2%80%98help%E2%80%99%20the%20state%20government%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20it%20failure%2C%20or%20unwillingness%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20said%20by%20veteran%20police%20officers%20and%20civil%20servants%20that%20if%20violence%2C%20especially%20communal%20violence%2C%20continues%20for%20more%20than%2024%20hours%2C%20it%20means%20the%20authorities%20do%20not%20want%20it%20to%20stop%20and%20are%20very%20much%20part%20of%20it.%20Imagine%20a%20whole%20state%20engulfed%20by%20sectarian%20violence%20for%20nearly%20three%20months!%20It%20was%20evident%20from%20day%20one%20that%20the%20state%20government%20was%20not%20too%20keen%20to%20stop%20the%20bloodshed.%20A%20government%20which%20justifies%20all%20its%20actions%20in%20the%20name%20of%20internal%20security%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20the%20control%20of%20the%20security%20of%20large%20areas%20of%20states%20which%20border%20other%20countries%2C%20allows%20a%20border%20state%20like%20Manipur%20to%20burn%20for%20three%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20must%20be%20a%20design%20behind%20this%20purported%20helplessness.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20we%20talk%20about%20it%2C%20we%20must%20also%20first%20describe%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20violence.%20Now%20all%20observers%20agree%20that%20Meitei%20majoritarian%20groups%20actively%20aided%20by%20the%20state%20police%2C%20have%20taken%20over%20the%20valley.%20There%20is%20no%20hiding%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%20is%20the%20patron%20of%20these%20groups.%C2%A0%20Their%20leaders%20have%20openly%20expressed%20their%20intent%20to%20exterminate%20the%20Kuki%20population.%20No%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20them.%20Are%20we%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20let%20them%20roam%20free%20is%20Biren%20Singhs%20alone%3F%20That%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20special%20representative%20sitting%20in%20Manipur%20cannot%20do%20anything%20to%20get%20the%20CM%20to%20reign%20these%20extremists%20in%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECould%20it%20be%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20like%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Imphal%2C%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20ending%20this%20majoritarian%20violence%3F%20That%20it%20wants%20this%20violence%20to%20run%20its%20course%20to%20achieve%20a%20definite%20purpose%3A%20of%20creating%20permanent%20division%20in%20Manipur%20so%20that%20it%20can%20better%20control%20the%20state%20and%20its%20resources%20by%20fragmenting%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-1024x513.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659017%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20crisis%20drags%20on%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20Manipur%20violence%20casting%20its%20malevolent%20shadows%20beyond%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20borders.%20The%20attack%20on%20Kukis%20had%20already%20created%20disquiet%20in%20Mizoram.%20Now%20we%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmeiteis-begin-to-leave-mizoram-after-threat-manipur-govt-says-willing-to-provide-flights-8855091%2F%5C%22%3Ethreats%20being%20issued%20to%20Meiteis%20in%20Mizoram%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20first%20and%20immediate%20response%20of%20the%20Manipur%20CM%20is%20to%20announce%20special%20plane%20services%20to%20evacuate%20Meiteis.%20Neither%20the%20state%2C%20nor%20the%20Union%20government%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20halt%20the%20violence%20and%20insecurity.%20After%20that%2C%20Meitei%20groups%20have%20issued%20threats%20to%20the%20Mizos%20living%20in%20the%20Barak%20valley%20of%20Assam.%20The%20Nagas%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20they%20should%20be%20left%20alone%2C%20are%20restless.%20In%20Meghalaya%2C%20in%20the%20very%20initial%20days%20of%20violence%2C%20local%20groups%20had%20said%20that%20people%20displaced%20from%20Manipur%20should%20not%20be%20given%20hospitality%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demand%20for%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20is%20being%20made%20by%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20it%20would%20definitely%20find%20an%20echo%20in%20other%20regions%20as%20all%20%E2%80%98natives%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%20people%20would%20want%20to%20secure%20their%20lands%20from%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20whole%20region%2C%20which%20was%20getting%20stable%20after%20decades%20of%20conflicts%2C%20has%20now%20been%20destabilised.%20It%20does%20not%20need%20great%20imagination%20to%20conclude%20that%20dormant%20militant%20factions%20will%20seek%20to%20regroup%20and%20rearm%20themselves%20with%20the%20support%20of%20their%20communities%C2%A0as%20they%20do%20not%20trust%20the%20state%20governments%20anymore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20ironic%20it%20is%20to%20see%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Social%20Powers%20Act(%20AFSPA)%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Manipuris%2C%20the%20very%20people%20who%20had%20been%20opposing%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%20for%20the%20last%20several%20decades.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20dangerously%20naive%20to%20think%20that%20all%20this%20is%20happening%20without%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Any%20government%20which%20cares%20for%20the%20nation%20would%20do%20everything%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20order%20in%20the%20country%20and%20society.%20But%20the%20record%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20one%20of%20creating%20chaos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChaos%2C%20uncertainty%20and%20instability%20are%20very%20helpful%20for%20authoritarian%20governments%20because%20they%20create%20confusion%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20people.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20fail%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20world%20around%20them%20and%20are%20numbed%20into%20silence.%20We%20have%20seen%20the%20Modi%20government%20destabilising%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%20through%20demonetisation%2C%20GST%20and%20the%20sudden%20lockdown.%20During%20the%20the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20we%20saw%20it%20controlling%20the%20supply%20of%20oxygen%2C%20making%20people%20run%20around%20in%20desperation%20and%20then%20entering%20the%20scene%20when%20chaos%20had%20run%20its%20course.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20instability%20and%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20is%20also%20good%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20as%20it%20can%20go%20to%20voters%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindi%20Belt%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20threat%20and%20a%20promise.%20The%20threat%20is%20of%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%20taking%20over%20the%20North%20East%20region%20and%20the%20promise%20is%20of%20controlling%20them.%20The%20figure%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98outsider%E2%80%99%20is%20what%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20wants%20to%20keep%20alive%20to%20scare%20the%20electorate%20into%20voting%20for%20it%20for%20their%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20PM%20but%20his%20refusal%20to%20end%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20which%20is%20proof%20of%20his%20complicity%20it%20it.%20One%20needs%20to%20note%20that%20in%20the%20first%20remarks%20on%20the%20crisis%20that%20he%20made%20in%2078%20days%2C%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20speak%20a%20word%20about%20Manipur%20itself%20but%20only%20about%20the%20incident%20related%20to%20the%20viral%20video.%20Taking%20a%20cue%20from%20him%2C%20top%20ministers%20and%20TV%20anchors%20have%20now%20made%20%E2%80%98violence%20against%20women%E2%80%99%20the%20issue%20and%20not%20the%20orchestrated%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20of%20which%20the%20horrific%20attack%20on%20women%20seen%20in%20that%20video%20is%20a%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20leads%20us%20to%20only%20one%20conclusion%3A%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20not%20at%20all%20bothered%20by%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Its%20silence%20and%20inaction%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20ongoing%20chaos%20is%20advantageous%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Who%20cares%20if%20India%20is%20cut%20to%20pieces%20and%20devoured%20by%20this%20majoritaria