the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20said%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.bwbx.io%2Fdocuments%2Fusers%2FiqjWHBFdfxIU%2FrlpoL.0rp2Vg%2Fv0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Lewis%20tipped%20off%20his%20acquaintances%20with%20inside%20information%20from%20publicly-traded%20companies%20in%20which%20he%20was%20a%20large%20investor%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20collectively%20make%20%26quot%3Bmillions%26quot%3B%20by%20trading%20securities%20before%20the%20information%20was%20disclosed%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDamian%20Williams%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20for%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSDNYnews%2Fstatus%2F1683958068395102208%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Lewis%20%26quot%3Babuses%20access%20to%20corporate%20boardrooms%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bcompensate%20his%20employees%20or%20to%20shower%20gifts%20on%20his%20friends%20and%20lovers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20classic%20corporate%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELewis%2C%20whose%20wealth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fbillionaires%2Fprofiles%2Fjoseph-c-lewis%2F%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20puts%20at%20%246.55%20billion%2C%20owns%20the%20Bahamas-based%20holding%20company%20Tavistock%20Group%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftavistock.com%2Fportfolio%2F%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20has%20investments%20in%20more%20than%20200%20companies%20including%20country%20clubs%2C%20real-estate%20developments%2C%20and%20a%20UK%20pub%20chain.%20Lewis%20also%20owns%20English%20soccer%20team%20Tottenham%20Hotspur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20made%20an%20egregious%20error%20in%20judgment%20in%20charging%20Mr.%20Lewis%2C%20an%2086-year-old%20man%20of%20impeccable%20integrity%20and%20prodigious%20accomplishment%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis's%20la