to%20be%2C%20maybe%2C%20slowly%20losing%20its%20prominence%20as%20the%20world's%20currency%2C%26quot%3B%20Peterffy%20said.%20The%20dollar%20could%20depreciate%20if%20the%20euro%20and%20Chinese%20renminbi%20become%20the%20go-to%20choices%20for%20overseas%20contracts%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECrypto%2C%20China%2C%20and%20call%20options%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Peterffy%20described%20his%20stance%20on%20cryptocurrencies%20as%20%26quot%3Bguarded%20skepticism%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20confirmed%20to%20MarketWatch%20that%20he%20still%20owns%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20it%20could%20become%20worthless%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20also%20possible%20that%20it%20will%20become%20very%20valuable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20electronic-trading%20pioneer%20%E2%80%94%20ranked%2060th%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fbillionaires%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20%2426%20billion%20fortune%20%E2%80%94%20also%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-economy-slowdown-slump-zero-covid-stock-market-crash-outlook-2023-6%5C%22%3Erecent%20signs%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20economic%20slowdown%20in%20China%2C%20arguing%20there's%20less%20risk%20now%20of%20the%20US%20losing%20ground%20its%20eastern%20rival.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Peterffy%20noted%20that%20many%20Interactive%20Brokers%20customers%20have%20made%20bank%20on%20Tesla%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20the%20other%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stocks-tesla-nvidia-apple-microsoft-amazon-the-magnificent-seven-2023-6%5C%22%3EMagnificent%20Seven%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20racked%20up%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20unrealized%20profits%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20are%20reluctant%20to%20cas