s%20and%20Adults%20only%20certificate%20for%20OMG%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690369016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102138675%2Cimgsize-30554.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frevising-committee-suggests-20-cuts-and-adults-only-certificate-for-omg-2%2Farticleshow%2F102139089.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102139089.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAfter%20being%20referred%20to%20Revising%20Committee%2C%20the%20board%20members%20given%20the%20content%20of%20the%20film%20have%20suggested%2020%20audio%20and%20visual%20cuts%20in%20the%20film%20and%20Adults%20only%20certificate%20for%20the%20film.%20The%20makers%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20suggestion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frevising-committee-suggests-20-cuts-and-adults-only-certificate-for-omg-2%2Farticleshow%2F102139089.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22If%20You%20Don't%20Trust...%5C%22%3A%20Court%20To%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Committee%20In%20Survey%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20survey%20by%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%2C%20the%20management%20committee%20of%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20today%20told%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20that%20it%20fears%20that%20the%20historic%20structure%20might%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20court%2C%20which%20asked%20the%20petitioners%20how%20they%20will%20trust%20the%20court's%20ruling%20if%20they%20cannot%20trust%20the%20ASI's%20assurances%20that%20there%20will%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaising%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20court%2C%20the%20mosque%20committee%20said%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20has%20stood%20at%20the%20place%2C%20next%20to%20the%20iconic%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20for%201%2C000%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20submissions%20that%20it%20trusts%20a%20survey%20similar%20to%20one%20that%20happened%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20case%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20mosque%20committee%C2%A0said%20the%20circumstances%20in%20the%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20dispute%20case%20were%20different%20and%20there%20cannot%20be%20a%20comparison%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20talk%20of%20a%20temple%20under%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20is%20fictional%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioners'%20counsel%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20imagination%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20allowing%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20ASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20side%20has%20claimed%20that%20a%20temple%20constructed%20at%20the%20site%20in%201585%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20Raja%20Todarmal%20was%20demolished%20in%201669.%20A%20group%20of%20Hindu%20women%20have%20now%20sought%20permission%20to%20worship%20the%20deities%20there%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20said%20that%20the%20women%20petitioners%20had%20told%20a%20lower%20court%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20proof%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20inside%20the%20mosque%20complex%20and%20that%20the%20ASI%20must%20gather%20them.%20%26quot%3BThis%20cannot%20be%20allowed.%20You%20cannot%20ask%20someone%20else%20to%20gather%20proof.%20This%20is%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20challenging%20the%20lower%20court's%20direction%20for%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20side%20stressed%20that%20they%20have%20proof%20and%20added%20that%20an%20ASI%20survey%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20expert%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asked%20the%20Hindu%20side%20if%20excavation%20was%20necessary%2C%20tits%20counsel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20but%20this%20won't%20be%20inside%20the%20mosque.%20ASI%20will%20do%20radar%20mapping.%20Excavation%20will%20also%20be%20conducted%20if%20circumstances%20demand%2C%20that%20too%20in%20the%20last%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20submissions%20on%20how%20this%20excavation%20will%20be%20conducted%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEither%20you%20videograph%20the%20survey%20or%20submit%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20mosque.%26quot%3B%20The%20Hindu%20side's%20counsel%20agreed%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20mosque%20committee%20said%20it%20does%20not%20trust%20the%20assurances%2C%20the%20court%20retorted%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20don't%20trust%20anyone%2C%20how%20will%20you%20trust%20our%20ruling%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20responded%20sharply%20to%20the%20mosque%20committee's%20submission%20that%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20lawyer%20would%20be%20responsible%20if%20the%20structure%20falls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asks%20if%20the%20mosque%20committee%20fears%20that%20the%20structure%20may%20fall%2C%20the%20committee%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20might%2C%20it%20is%201%2C000%20years%20old.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20assurances%20that%20no%20survey%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20area%20sealed%20under%20orders%20from%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20mosque%20committee%20said%20that%20area%20will%20also%20suffer%20damage%20if%20the%20survey%20is%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20submission%20that%20the%20ASI%20team%20is%20waiting%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20satisfied%20with%20what%20you%20are%20going%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20submission%20that%20the%20structure%20won't%20be%20damaged%2C%20he%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20going%20to%20drill%20or%20is%20it%20like%20a%20vacuum%20cleaner%3F%20Have%20you%20ever%20done%20this%20work%20earlier%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20ASI%20said%20they%20have%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%20if%20there%20are%20photos%20of%20those%20projects.%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20is%20putting%20strong%20doubts%20to%20the%20work%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20side%20said%20the%20machine%20used%20%26quot%3Bwill%20move%20like%20a%20lawn%20mower%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20machines%20are%20accepted%20all%20over%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20resume%20the%20hearing%20at%204.30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20hit%20headlines%20in%202021%20after%20a%20group%20of%20Hindu%20women%20approached%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20court%20for%20permission%20to%20worship%20deities%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lower%20court%20then%20ordered%20a%20video%20survey%20of%20the%20complex%20during%20which%20an%20object%20was%20discovered%20that%20a%20section%20of%20people%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20shivling.%20The%20mosque%20management%20committee%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20fountain%20in%20the%20wazookhana%20(pool)%20to%20wash%20hands%20and%20feet%20before%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20issue%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20sealed%20off%20the%20pool%20(wazookhana).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20mosque%20committee's%20petition%20that%20challenge%20the%20maintainability%20of%20the%20request%20to%20worship%20Hindu%20deities%20found%20inside%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20a%20Varanasi%20court's%20ruling%2C%20allowing%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20ASI%20inside%20the%20mosque%20complex%20except%20the%20pool%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20expressing%20concerns%20regarding%20excavation%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20now%20allowed%20the%20petitioners%20to%20approach%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20to%20challenge%20the%20order%20for%20the%20ASI%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690368900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F6tbusq7o_gyanvapi-mosque-650_625x300_13_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-fears-4240992%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20survey%20by%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%2C%20the%20management%20committee%20of%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20today%20told%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20that%20it%20fears%20that%20the%20historic%20structure%20might%20fall.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-fears-4240992%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-fears-4240992%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-fears-4240992%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Messi's%20kind%20gesture%20towards%20Beckham%20goes%20viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690368884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102138932%2Cimgsize-52940.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Ffootball%2Ftop-stories%2Fwatch-lionel-messis-kind-gesture-towards-david-beckham-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F102138867.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lionel%20Messi%20continues%20to%20make%20his%20presence%20felt%20in%20the%20United%20States%20with%20yet%20another%20match%20winning%20performance%20for%20Inter%20Miami%20but%20what%20stole%20the%20limelight%20more%20than%20the%20result%20was%20his%20gesture%20towards%20the%20club's%20co-owner%20David%20Beckham%20after%20scoring%20a%20goal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Ffootball%2Ftop-stories%2Fwatch-lionel-messis-kind-gesture-towards-david-beckham-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F102138867.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20Classic%20Psychology%20Warped%20Our%20View%20of%20Human%20Nature%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26143853%2F06f6c811db2dec276447b8c92f50-1452799.jpgd_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20classic%20experiments%20and%20theories%20that%20every%20psychology%20student%20learns%20about%2C%20but%20more%20recent%20research%20has%20questioned%20their%20findings%20so%20that%20psychologists%20today%20are%20reevaluating%20human%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20Philip%20Zimbardo%E2%80%99s%201971%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fexhibits.stanford.edu%2Fspe%5C%22%3EStanford%20prison%20experiment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%2024%20participants%20were%20randomly%20separated%20into%20groups%20of%20would-be%20prisoners%20and%20guards.%20Within%20days%2C%20the%20research%20recorded%20that%20the%20guards%20were%20mistreating%20the%20prisoners%2C%20who%20began%20to%20display%20signs%20of%20distress.%20The%20abuse%20and%20distress%20became%20seemed%20so%20acute%20the%20experiment%20had%20to%20be%20curtailed%20after%20six%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20classic%20psychological%20theory%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscientist.com%2Farticle%2F2207693-bystander-effect-famous-psychology-result-could-be-completely-wrong%2F%5C%22%3Ebystander%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20suggests%20that%20people%20are%20reluctant%20to%20help%20out%20in%20emergency%20situations%20if%20others%20are%20nearby.%20This%20theory%20dates%20back%20to%201964%2C%20when%20a%20woman%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20the%20early%20morning%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20reported%20that%2038%20people%20witnessed%20the%20attack%2C%20without%20intervening.%20According%20to%20the%20bystander%20effect%2C%20the%20more%20people%20that%20witness%20an%20event%2C%20the%20less%20likely%20a%20person%20is%20to%20intervene%2C%20since%20responsibility%20becomes%20more%20diffused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20theories%20and%20studies%20from%20the%201960s%20and%201970s%20implied%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cevil%E2%80%9D%20sides%20of%20our%20character%20lie%20just%20below%20our%20civilised%20surface%2C%20while%20the%20moral%20and%20altruistic%20side%20is%20a%20thin%20veneer.%20They%20encouraged%20a%20view%20that%20human%20beings%20are%20essentially%20callous%20and%20selfish.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20findings%20of%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.st-andrews.ac.uk%2Farchive%2Fresearchers-call-for-open-and-respectful-debate-around-stanford-prison-experiment%2F%5C%22%3Eexperiments%20have%20now%20been%20contested%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20discredited%20by%20other%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgen.medium.com%2Fthe-lifespan-of-a-lie-d869212b1f62%5C%22%3ERecent%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fetheses.whiterose.ac.uk%2F32348%2F1%2FAnderson_205052450_CorrectedThesisClean.pdf%5C%22%3Ecruelty%20of%20Zimbardo%E2%80%99s%20prison%20guards%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20emerge%20spontaneously%3B%20some%20behaviour%20was%20encouraged.%20Some%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprisoners%E2%80%9D%20later%20admitted%20that%20they%20were%20pretending%20to%20be%20distressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20a%20study%20published%20in%202007%20found%20that%20the%201964%20incident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F17874896%2F%5C%22%3Ethat%20inspired%20the%20theory%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%3Cbr%3E%5Cnbystander%20effect%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffee.org%2Farticles%2Fthe-bystander-effect-myth-or-fact%2F%5C%22%3Edistorted%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20paper%2C%20archive%20material%20shows%20far%20fewer%20people%20witnessed%20the%20incident%20than%20was%20reported%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20some%20people%20could%20only%20hear%20screams%2C%20without%20seeing%20the%20location%20of%20the%20incident.%20At%20least%20one%20person%20did%20try%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20research%20indicates%20that%20bystanders%20are%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20intervene%20than%20the%20theory%20suggests.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2FdoiLanding%3Fdoi%3D10.1037%252Famp0000469%5C%22%3E2019%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20219%20violent%20situations%20from%20cities%20around%20the%20world%20caught%20on%20CCTV%20showed%20that%20bystanders%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20one%2C%20usually%20several%20%E2%80%93%20intervened%20to%20help%20victims%2090%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20the%20more%20people%20were%20present%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20passers-by%20were%20to%20intervene.%20In%20the%20words%20of%20the%20study%E2%80%99s%20lead%20researcher%2C%20Richard%20Philpot%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20that%20people%20have%20a%20natural%20inclination%20to%20help%20when%20they%20see%20someone%20in%20need.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeroism%20and%20altruism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20burgeoning%20field%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholarship.richmond.edu%2Fheroism-science%2F%5C%22%3Eheroism%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20also%20questions%20the%20bystander%20effect.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhow-the-manchester-arena-attack-showed-that-altruism-is-human-instinct-204430%5C%22%3Erecent%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20The%20Conversation%2C%20I%20described%20how%20acts%20of%20heroic%20altruism%20are%20common%20during%20terrorist%20attacks%2C%20when%20people%20often%20risk%20their%20own%20lives%20to%20help%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20the%20following%20situation%3A%20you%E2%80%99re%20standing%20on%20a%20train%20platform.%20The%20person%20next%20to%20you%20suddenly%20faints%20and%20falls%20on%20to%20the%20track%2C%20unconscious.%20In%20the%20distance%2C%20you%20can%20see%20a%20train%20approaching.%20What%20would%20you%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20doubt%20whether%20you%20would%20act%20heroically.%20But%20don%E2%80%99t%3Cbr%3E%5Cnunderestimate%20yourself.%20There%20is%20a%20strong%20possibility%20that%2C%20before%20you%20knew%20it%2C%20you%20would%20find%20yourself%20on%20down%20on%20the%20track%2C%20helping%20the%20person%20to%20safety.%20There%20is%20a%20growing%20awareness%20amongst%20researchers%20that%20heroism%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fplosone%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0109687%5C%22%3Enatural%20and%20spontaneous%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6449723%2F%5C%22%3Eno%20means%20exceptional%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FlokQ9cNqAV8%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22260%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20%E2%80%9Cperson%20jumps%20down%20on%20to%20train%20track%20to%20save%20life%E2%80%9D%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20dozens%20of%20cases%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20some%20moving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ_XU37ZArmo%5C%22%3Evideo%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlokQ9cNqAV8%5C%22%3Erecent%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20New%20York%20City%20subway%2C%20when%20a%20wheelchair-bound%20man%20fell%20on%20to%20the%20track.%20A%20bystander%20jumps%20down%2C%20pushes%20the%20wheelchair%20to%20one%20side%2C%20and%20hauls%20the%20man%20up%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20others%20on%20the%20platform.%20A%20train%20arrived%20ten%20seconds%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D72-obuscJ-E%5C%22%3EAnother%20dramatic%20video%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnshows%20an%20incident%20in%202015%2C%20when%20a%20cyclist%20was%20trapped%20under%20the%20wheel%20of%20a%20doubledecker%20bus%20in%20London.%20A%20crowd%20of%20around%20100%20people%20gathered%2C%20and%20lifted%20the%20bus.%20According%20to%20a%20paramedic%20who%20treated%20the%20man%2C%20this%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%E2%80%9D%20which%20may%20have%20saved%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7lciE6onOc8%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22260%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20point%20out%20in%20my%20book%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stevenmtaylor.com%2Fbooks%2Fdisconnected%2F%5C%22%3EDisConnected%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20acts%20of%20impulsive%20altruism%20suggest%20an%20empathic%20connection%20between%20human%20beings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20view%20of%20human%20nature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20view%2C%20early%20psychologists%20may%20have%20been%20unconsciously%20tailoring%20their%20experiments%20to%20confirm%20a%20view%20of%20human%20nature%20as%20innately%20cruel.%20These%20studies%20were%20carried%20out%20less%20than%2020%20years%20after%20the%20second%20world%20war%20and%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20when%20the%20horrors%20of%20WWII%20were%20still%20fresh%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20genetic%20theories%20were%20published%20that%20suggested%20that%20human%20beings%20are%20biological%20engines%2C%20caring%20for%20nothing%20but%20replication%20and%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%201976%2C%20Richard%20Dawkins%E2%80%99%20book%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.oup.com%2Facademic%2Fproduct%2Fthe-selfish-gene-9780198788607%3Fcc%3Dgb%26lang%3Den%26%5C%22%3EThe%20Selfish%20Gene%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20published%2C%20which%20portrayed%20human%20beings%20as%20%E2%80%9Csurvival%20machines%E2%80%9D%20who%20treat%20other%20survival%20machines%20as%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20that%20gets%20in%20the%20way%2C%20or%20something%20that%20can%20be%20exploited%E2%80%9D.%20He%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20try%20to%20teach%20generosity%20and%20altruism%2C%20because%20we%20are%20born%20selfish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20research%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20areas%20points%20to%20a%20more%20positive%20view%20of%20humanity.%20Along%20with%20the%20study%20of%20heroism%2C%20the%20field%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpositivepsychology.com%2Fwhat-is-positive-psychology-definition%2F%5C%22%3Epositive%20psychology%3C%2Fa%3E%20(established%20during%20the%20early%202000s)%20studies%20human%20wellbeing%20and%20researches%20traits%20such%20as%20wisdom%2C%20courage%2C%20gratitude%20and%20resilience.%20Positive%20psychologists%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpositivepsychology.com%2Fpositive-psychology-theory%2F%5C%22%3EMartin%20Seligman%3C%2Fa%3E%20argue%20conventional%20psychology%20had%20for%20too%20long%20been%20essentially%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20study%20of%20unhappiness%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20a%20new%20field%20was%20needed%20to%20study%20what%20%E2%80%9Cis%20good%20or%20virtuous%20in%20human%20nature%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consensus%20from%20anthropologists%20is%20that%2C%20for%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20time%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20inhabited%20this%20planet%2C%20human%20societies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwhy-our-ancestors-were-more-gender-equal-than-us-41902%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20egalitarian%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.scientificamerican.com%2Fcross-check%2Fnew-study-of-prehistoric-skeletons-undermines-claim-that-war-has-deep-evolutionary-roots%2F%5C%22%3Epeaceful%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20challenges%20the%20neo-Darwinist%20idea%20that%20human%20life%20has%20always%20been%20a%20competitive%20struggle%20for%20survival%2C%20conditioning%20us%20to%20be%20selfish%20and%20individualistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20forerunner%20of%20positive%20psychology%2C%20Abraham%20Maslow%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.positivedisintegration.com%2Fmasid.htm%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%201968%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20human%20nature%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Csold%20short%E2%80%9D%20by%20psychology.%20Human%20beings%20can%20be%20brutal%20and%20selfish.%20But%20we%20can%20be%20heroically%20kindhearted%20too.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F209991%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESteve%20Taylor%2C%20Senior%20Lecturer%20in%20Psychology%2C%20Leeds%20Beckett%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhow-classic-psychology-warped-our-view-of-human-nature-as-cruel-and-selfish-but-new-research-is-more-hopeful-209991%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690368878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26143853%2F06f6c811db2dec276447b8c92f50-1452799.jpgd_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fhas-classic-psychology-warped-our-view-of-human-nature%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recent%20research%20challenges%20classic%20psychology%20experiments%2C%20revealing%20humanity's%20innate%20capacity%20for%20heroism%20and%20altruism.%20Positive%20psychology%20and%20anthropological%20consensus%20support%20a%20more%20positive%20view%20of%20human%20nature%2C%20embracing%20kindness%20and%20compassion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fhas-classic-psychology-warped-our-view-of-human-nature%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20Phangnon%20Konyak%2C%20MP%20Who%20Created%20History%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%3F%205%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20April%202022%2C%20Ms%20Konyak%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20be%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Nagaland%20and%20the%20second%20woman%20from%20the%20state%20to%20be%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20or%20the%20state%20Assembly.%20She%20followed%20Rano%20M%20Shaiza%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%201977.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Konyak%20hails%20from%20Dimapur%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20where%20she%20completed%20her%20schooling.%20She%20then%20moved%20to%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20pursued%20a%20Master's%20Degree%20in%20English%20Literature%20from%20Daulat%20Ram%20College%2C%20which%20is%20affiliated%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20tweet%20after%20presiding%20over%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BImmensely%20privileged%2C%20humbled%20and%20overwhelmed%20to%20preside%20over%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today.%20Happy%20that%20it%20was