ther%20it%20is%20rare%20or%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1683852156749729793%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20reports%2C%20the%20condition%20of%20Bronny%20is%20said%20to%20be%20stable%20and%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20longer%20in%20ICU.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20while%20practicing%20Bronny%20James%20suffered%20a%20cardiac%20arrest.%20Medical%20staff%20was%20able%20to%20treat%20Bronny%20and%20take%20him%20to%20the%20hospital.%20He%20is%20now%20in%20stable%20condition%20and%20no%20longer%20in%20ICU%20(intensive%20care)%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20James%20family%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20ask%20for%20respect%20and%20privacy%20for%20the%20James%20family%20and%20we%20will%20update%20media%20when%20there%20is%20more%20information.%20LeBron%20and%20Savannah%20wish%20to%20publicly%20send%20their%20deepest%20thanks%20and%20appreciation%20to%20the%20USC%20medical%20and%20athletic%20staff%20for%20their%20incredible%20work%20and%20dedication%20to%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20athletes%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20American%20Heart%20Association%2C%20only%20about%201%20in%2010%20people%20survive%20an%20out-of-hospital%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20which%20occurs%20when%20the%20heart%20stops%20abruptly%20with%20little%20or%20no%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJames'%20cardiac%20arrest%20came%20just%20over%20a%20year%20after%20another%20USC%20basketball%20player%2C%20Vince%20Iwuchukwu%2C%20suffered%20heart%20failure%20and%20collapsed%20during%20an%20informal%20practice.%20Iwuchukwu%20subsequently%20made%20a%20full%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20AFP%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690368600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2