e-combat-2023-1%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20if%20Russia%20does%20deploy%20the%20T-14%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20likely%20primarily%20be%20for%20propaganda%20purposes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProduction%20is%20probably%20only%20in%20the%20low%20tens%2C%20while%20commanders%20are%20unlikely%20to%20trust%20the%20vehicle%20in%20combat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20citing%20intelligence%20sources%20and%20satellite%20imagery.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tank%20was%20first%20unveiled%20at%20Russia's%20Victory%20Day%20Parade%20on%20May%209%2C%202015%2C%20but%20its%20roll-out%20has%20been%20plagued%20with%20delays%20and%20technical%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20initially%20planned%20for%202%2C300%20of%20the%20tanks%20to%20arrive%20between%202015%20and%202020.%20But%20in%20December%202021%2C%20the%20Russian%20conglomerate%20Rostec%20said%20production%20of%20around%2040%20tanks%20had%20only%20just%20started%2C%20and%20that%20they%20were%20anticipated%20for%20delivery%20after%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interfax.ru%2Frussia%2F812466%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%2293c93ee70665da1993a9dcf341d81cca%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interfax.ru%2Frussia%2F812466%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Russian%20news%20agency%20Interfax.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20necessary%20trials%20of%20the%20T-14%20tank%20still%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20unnamed%20military%20source%20told%20TASS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-deployed-t-14-tanks-ukraine-but-then-withdrew-them-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690367208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insid