p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20Moroccan%20society%E2%80%99s%20perceptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2045%2C000%20fans%20packed%20out%20the%20Moulay%20Abdellah%20Stadium%20for%20the%202022%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Africa%20Cup%20of%20Nations%20(WAFCON)%20final%20in%20Morocco%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Rabat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hosts%20weren%E2%80%99t%20supposed%20to%20be%20there%2C%20but%20pulled%20off%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcould-moroccos-wafcon-success-jumpstart-womens-football-in-the-arab-world%2Fa-62971926%5C%22%3Eshock%20win%20against%2011-time%20winners%20Nigeria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20semifinals.%20They%20lost%20the%20final%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsouth-africas-wafcon-victory-inspires-pay-parity-calls%2Fa-62624638%5C%22%3E2-1%20against%20South%20Africa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20represented%20a%20massive%20shift%20for%20Chebbak%2C%20who%20won%20player%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThings%20have%20changed%20since%20the%20WAFCON.%20We%20managed%20to%20change%20society%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20at%20that%20tournament%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fans%E2%80%99%20love%20is%20really%20encouraging%20and%20gives%20us%20motivation%20to%20continue%20our%20work.%20And%20the%20Moroccan%20FA%20is%20making%20huge%20efforts%20to%20provide%20the%20necessary%20conditions.%20It%20may%20take%20time%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99m%20convinced%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20will%20shine%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeavy%20investment%20and%20a%20coaching%20group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Moroccan%20Football%20Association%20has%20invested%20in%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20game%20since%202009%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20rapid%20transformation%20since%20president%20Fouzi%20Lekjaa%20kickstarted%20a%20four-year%20plan%20in%202020%20with%20support%20from%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20monarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20professionalized%20the%20top%20two%20divisions%2C%20provided%20set%20minimum%20wages%20for%20players%20and%20the%20staff%20of%20all%20clubs%2C%20and%20bolstered%20grassroots%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHiring%20Reynald%20Pedros%20was%20another%20masterstroke.%20The%20French%20coach%20won%20two%20women%E2%80%99s%20Champions%20League%20titles%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwomens-champions-league-lyon-retake-european-throne-on-night-of-historic-support%2Fa-61890010%5C%22%3Epowerhouses%20Olympique%20Lyon%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20quickly%20reshaped%20the%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPedros%20introduced%C2%A0training%20standards%20and%C2%A0tactics%20and%20player%20confidence%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20achievements%20are%20the%20result%20of%20continuous%20work%20over%20the%20years.%20We%20had%20big%20ambitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chebbak%20said.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%E2%80%99re%20concentrating%20on%20the%20World%20Cup.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorocco%20will%20rely%20on%20foreign-born%20talent%20with%20Moroccan%20roots%20at%20this%20tournament%20with%20Rosella%20Ayane%20(England)%2C%20Yasmin%20Mrabet%20(Spain)%20and%20Elodie%20Nakkach%20(France)%20playing%20vital%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20professionalisation%20of%20the%20domestic%20leagues%20should%20be%20the%20bedrock%20for%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShifting%20opinions%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20sport%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChabbak%20was%20fortunate%20that%20her%20family%20were%20always%20supportive%20of%20her%20dream%20to%20play%20professional%20football%2C%20particularly%20her%20father%2C%20Larbi%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20football-loving%20family%20who%20supported%20and%20advised%20me.%20My%20father%20always%20provided%20me%20with%20guidance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThankfully%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20I%20made%20him%20proud%20and%20I%20want%20to%20make%20him%20even%20prouder.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20weren%E2%80%99t%20so%20fortunate%2C%20facing%20opposition%20from%20their%20community%20and%20even%20their%20own%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20lost%20many%20talents%20due%20to%20societal%20views%20and%20families%E2%80%99%20rejection%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chebbak%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20many%20talented%20players%20who%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20go%20far.%20But%20families%20were%20afraid%20of%20allowing%20their%20daughters%20to%20play%20football%20and%20prevented%20them%20from%20doing%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGermany%20are%20Morocco%E2%80%99s%20first%20opponents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20so%20proud%20to%20witness%20these%20achievements%20and%20see%20Morocco%20contribute%20to%20the%20growth%20and%20recognition%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bouchti%2C%20who%20travelled%20to%20Melbourne%20to%20attend%20the%20opener%20against%20Germany.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20want%20to%20thank%20them%20for%20raising%20our%20flag%20and%20making%20us%20very%20proud.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20H%20isn%E2%80%99t%20set%20to%20get%20much%20easier%20with%20games%20against%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-cup-casey-phair-makes-south-korean-football-history%2Fa-66294107%5C%22%3ESouth%20Korea%20and%20Colombia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20confidence%20running%20through%20this%20team%20should%20help%20them%20achieve%20their%20lofty%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20incredible%20to%20qualify%20but%20now%20our%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chebbak%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20it%20will%20be%20challenging%20but%20we%20will%20concentrate%20on%20our%20style%20of%20play.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20co