20from%20the%20firm's%20current%20funds%20and%20the%20new%20capital%20raised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20many%20VCs%20and%20their%20firms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiger-global-hedge-fund-cut-back-fundraising-2023-7%3Finline-endstory-related-recommendations%3D%5C%22%3ETiger%20Global%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20TCV%20and%20Insight%20Partners%2C%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fventure-capitalists-not-making-fundraising-goals-this-year-2023-6%5C%22%3Etempering%20their%20lofty%20fundraising%20goals%20by%20lowering%20their%20targets%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20capital%20has%20put%20Mayfield%20in%20a%20position%20to%20lean%20in%20and%20do%20more%20investments%20than%20it%20typically%20does.%20The%20firm%20does%20about%20eight%20investments%20per%20year%20and%20when%20markets%20get%20too%20frothy%2C%20Mayfield%20actually%20pulls%20back%20on%20investing%20%E2%80%93%20like%20it%20did%20in%202021%20when%20it%20only%20invested%20in%20seven%20new%20startups%2C%20Chaddha%20said.%20But%20now%20that%20the%20market%20has%20been%20on%20shaky%20footing%20the%20past%20year%20with%20talks%20of%20a%20looming%20recession%2C%20Mayfield's%20leader%2C%20Navin%20Chaddha%2C%20says%20the%20firm%20is%20probably%20on%20pace%20to%20do%20up%20to%2015%20new%20investments%20this%20year.%20Last%20year%2C%20when%20most%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-industry-cost-cutting-job-losses-whos-most-at-risk-2022-5%5C%22%3Eventure%20industry%20pulled%20back%20on%20funding%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mayfield%20made%2012%20new%20investments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20what%20we%20do%2C%20when%20things%20get%20out%20of%20whack%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20industry%20follows%20this%20way%2C%20we%20follow%20that%20way.%20We%20are%20just%20contrarian%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaddha%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20timing%20really%20