%20our%20PM%20(Pratham%20Sevak)%20was%20conferred%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-order-of-the-nile-all-state-honours-list-8685506%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Order%20of%20the%20Nile%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fpm-modi-conferred-with-frances-highest-award-grand-cross-of-the-legion-of-honour%2Farticle67078793.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPrime%2520Minister%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2520has%2Cby%2520French%2520President%2520Emmanuel%2520Macron.%5C%22%3EFrench%20Legion%20of%20Honour%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20joyfully%20given%2C%20joyfully%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20beleaguered%20state%20of%20Manipur%20some%20rioters%20were%20issued%20warrants%20and%20hauled%20to%20prisons.%20Who%20were%20they%3F%20What%20sections%20were%20slapped%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnarendra-modi-islamic-nations-egypt-eid-gujarat-lynching%5C%22%3EEgypt%E2%80%99s%20Paeans%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20Cannot%20Erase%20the%20Past%20or%20Present%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20nation%20I%20feel%20we%20must%20demand%20%E2%80%98command%20responsibility.%E2%80%99%20This%20concept%20is%20used%20in%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice.%20Responsibility%20lies%20with%20the%20highest%20authority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiving%20life%20sentences%2C%20even%20hanging%20a%20few%20is%20relatively%20easy.%20They%20are%20the%20rogue%20perpetrators.%20But%20their%20strings%20are%20held%20by%20those%20at%20the%20pinnacle.%20By%20shouting%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhoon%20ka%20badla%20khoon%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20rooftops%20we%2C%20the%20masses%20cannot%20be%20lulled%3B%20we%20are%20alive%20and%20awake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E*%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20is%20the%20land%20which%20gave%20birth%20to%20Polo%2C%20Sagol%20Kangjei%2C%20in%20ancient%20days.%20In%201799%20to%20it%20birthed%20Rasleela.%20I%20remember%20watching%20a%20breathtaking%20performance%20in%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Jewel%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%99%20encircled%20by%20nine%20hills%20with%20an%20oval%20shaped%20valley%20in%20the%20centre.%20I%20walked%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Manipur%20at%20the%20time%20of%20Kangla%20festivities%20as%20well%20as%20the%20time%20when%20Thangjam%20Manorma%20was%20gang%20raped%20and%20killed%20and%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20stripped%20before%20the%20garrison%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FManipur-mothers-reuters.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22621%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-117721%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMeira%20Paibis%20protesting%20against%20Afspa%20in%20Imphal%20in%202004.%20Photo%3A%20Reuters%2FFiles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20brought%20a%20delegation%20of%20six%20Meira%20Paibis%20to%20meet%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20in%20the%20evening%20after%20he%20had%20dedicated%20Kangla.%20The%C2%A0%20Assam%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20comment%20reported%20in%20the%20media%20about%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur-was-blockade-capital-under-manmohan-singh-state-healing-due-to-pm-modi-assam-cm-himanta-biswa-sarma%2Farticleshow%2F102043363.cms%5C%22%3Etremendous%20healing%20in%20Manipur%20since%202014%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20snide%20comment%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20reflects%20his%20ignorance%20of%20even%20recent%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20book%20which%20I%20co-authored%20with%20Gunjan%20Veda%2C%20we%20wrote%20of%20the%20Manipur%20we%20saw%20when%20Singh%20was%20PM.%20%E2%80%98That%20evening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20we%20saw%20a%20smiling%20Manipur%2C%20a%20joyous%20Manipur.%20As%20the%20ecstatic%20crowds%20swept%20us%20out%20of%20the%20Kangla%20premises%2C%20we%20realized%20that%20we%20had%20seen%20history%20in%20the%20making%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Manipur%20let%20the%20ordinary%20women%20and%20men%20of%20India%20demand%20%E2%80%98command%20responsibility.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E*%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20days%20some%20of%20us%20are%20commemorating%20Moharrum%2C%20among%20the%20most%20profound%20tragedies%20in%20recorded%20history%2C%20which%20happened%20in%20Karbala%201%2C343%20years%20ago.%20What%20has%20happened%20in%20Manipur%20and%20is%20spreading%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20Assam%20and%20Meghalaya%20felt%20like%20another%20Karbala%20to%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20healers%20and%20mourners%2C%20we%20want%20to%20place%20our%20loving%20hands%20on%20the%20wounds%20inflicted%20on%20our%20Manipur%20sisters%20and%20brothers.%20Imphal%2C%20Bishnupur%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20Thoubal%2C%20Senapati%3B%20where%20to%20date%20there%20have%20been%20at%20least%20150%20deaths%2C%201%2C000%20injured%20and%2050%2C000%20homeless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20just%20one%20goal%20and%20an%20arduous%20path%20to%20tread.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20words%20of%20Faiz%20Ahmed%20Faiz%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKat-te%20bhi%20chalo%20badhte%20bhi%20chalo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBaazu%20bhi%20bahaut%20hain%20sar%20bhi%20bahaut%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EChalte%20bhi%20chalo%20ke%20ab%20derey%3C%2Fspan%3