s%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22093319%2FFzKsbspXoAcEw_0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22093319%2FFzKsbspXoAcEw_0.jpeg%20706w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F22093319%2FFzKsbspXoAcEw_0-300x188.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20photo%2C%20purportedly%20of%20an%20IED%20blast%20site%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Bishnupur%2C%20circulating%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nation%20has%20risen%3B%20protests%2C%20marches%2C%20statements%2C%20petitions%20pour%20in%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20the%20country%2C%20even%20places%20where%20Manipur%20was%20barely%20known.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20world%20bodies%20woke%20up%20and%20indictments%20began%20pouring%20in%20from%20USA%20and%20Europe.%20Some%20nations%20urged%20India%20to%20stop%20this%20horror.%20Demurely%20we%20said%20to%20Christian%20nations%2C%20%E2%80%98Violence%20in%20Manipur%20is%20not%20religious.%20In%20any%20event%20it%E2%80%99s%20our%20internal%20matter%20so%20mind%20your%20own%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20in%20Egypt%20and%20France%20our%20PM%20(Pratham%20Sevak)%20was%20conferred%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-order-of-the-nile-all-state-honours-list-8685506%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Order%20of%20the%20Nile%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fpm-modi-conferred-with-frances-highest-award-grand-cross-of-the-legion-of-honour%2Farticle67078793.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPrime%2520Minister%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2520has%2Cby%2520French%2520President%2520Emmanuel%2520Macron.%5C%22%3EFrench%20Legion%20of%20Honour%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20joyfully%20given%2C%20joyfully%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20beleaguered%20state%20of%20Manipur%20some%20rioters%20were%20issued%20warrants%20and%20hauled%20to%20prisons.%20Who%20were%20they%3F%20What%20sections%20were%20slapped%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnarendra-modi-islamic-nations-egypt-eid-gujarat-lynching%5C%22%3EEgypt%E2%80%99s%20Paeans%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20Cannot%20Erase%20the%20Past%20or%20Present%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20nation%20I%20feel%20we%20must%20demand%20%E2%80%98command%20responsibility.%E2%80%99%20This%20concept%20is%20used%20in%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice.%20Responsibility%20lies%20with%20the%20highest%20authority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiving%20life%20sentences%2C%20even%20hanging%20a%20few%20is%20relatively%20easy.%20They%20are%20the%20rogue%20perpetrators.%20But%20their%20strings%20are%20held%20by%20those%20at%20the%20pinnacle.%20By%20shouting%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhoon%20ka%20badla%20khoon%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20rooftops%20we%2C%20the%20masses%20cannot%20be%20lulled%3B%20we%20are%20alive%20and%20awake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E*%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20is%20the%20land%20which%20gave%20birth%20to%20Polo%2C%20Sagol%20Kangjei%2C%20in%20ancient%20days.%20In%201799%20to%20it%20birthed%20Rasleela.%20I%20remember%20watching%20a%20breathtaking%20performance%20in%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Jewel%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%99%20encircled%20by%20nine%20hills%20with%20an%20oval%20shaped%20valley%20in%20the%20centre.%20I%20walked%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Manipur%20at%20the%20time%20of%20Kangla%20festivities%20as%20well%20as%20the%20time%20when%20Thangjam%20Manorma%20was%20gang%20raped%20and%20killed%20and%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20stripped%20before%20the%20garrison%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FManipur-mothers-reuters.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22621%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-117721%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMeira%20Paibis%20protesting%20against%20Afspa%20in%20Imphal%20in%202004.%20Photo%3A%20Reuters%2FFiles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20brought%20a%20delegation%20of%20six%20Meira%20Paibis%20to%20meet%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20in%20the%20evening%20after%20he%20had%20dedicated%20Kangla.%20The%C2%A0%20Assam%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20comment%20reported%20in%20the%20media%20about%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur-was-blockade-capital-under-manmohan-singh-state-healing-due-to-pm-modi-assam-cm-himanta-biswa-sarma%2Farticleshow%2F102043363.cms%5C%22%3Etremendous%20healing%20in%20Manipur%20since%202014%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20snide%20comment%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20reflects%20his%20ignorance%20of%20even%20recent%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20book%20which%20I%20co-authored%20with%20Gunjan%20Veda%2C%20we%20wrote%20of%20the%20Manipur%20we%20saw%20when%20Singh%20was%20PM.%20%E2%80%98That%20evening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20we%20saw%20a%20smiling%20Manipur%2C%20a%20joyous%20Manipur.%20As%20the%20ecstatic%20crowds%20swept%20us%20out%20of%20the%20Kangla%20premises%2C%20we%20realized%20that%20we%20had%20seen%20history%20in%20the%20making%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Manipur%20let%20the%20ordinary%20women%20and%20men%20of%20India%20demand%20%E2%80%98command%20responsibility.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E*%3C%2Fspa