0196e32b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223392%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQin%20Gang%20(above)%20was%20removed%20from%20his%20position%20as%20China's%20foreign%20minister%20on%20Tuesday.%3Cp%3EThomas%20Trutschel%2FPhotothek%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opacity%20of%20China's%20government%20means%20we%20may%20never%20know%20why%20Qin%20Gang%20was%20ousted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEurasia%20Group's%20Jeremy%20Chan%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%20remains%20unknown%20about%20Qin's%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReferences%20to%20Qin%20have%20already%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20foreign%20ministry's%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20month%20after%20he%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20public%2C%20Qin%20Gang%20was%20removed%20from%20his%20post%20as%20China's%20foreign%20minister.%20The%20news%20sent%20shockwaves%20around%20the%20world%2C%20but%20it%20came%20with%20no%20explanation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20experts%20say%20we%20may%20never%20get%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20China's%20state-run%20press%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.news.cn%2F20230725%2F63acc0b9907a416baa336b5e777a4aaa%2Fc.html%5C%22%3EXinhua%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20simply%20that%20the%20country's%20%26quot%3Btop%20legislature%20voted%20to%20appoint%20Wang%20Yi%20as%20foreign%20minister%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3BQin%20Gang%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20post.%26quot%3B%20Wang%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-appoints-wang-yi-its-new-foreign-minister-replacing-absent-qin-gang-2023-07-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20held%20the%20role%20of%20foreign%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202013%20to%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20press%20time%2C%20references%20to%20Qin%20had%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20foreign%20ministry's%20website.%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%20opacity%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20few%20people%20will%20ever%20know%20what%20led%20to%20Qin's%20abrupt%20departure%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20much%20remains%20unknown%20about%20Qin's%20case%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20with%20precision%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeremy%20Chan%2C%20a%20consultant%20for%20Eurasia%20Group%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20government%20has%20handled%20the%20Qin%20affair%20so%20far%20indicates%20that%20we%20are%20unlikely%20to%20ever%20get%20a%20full%20accounting%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20his%20disappearance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChong%20Ja%20Ian%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20%26quot%3Bis%20part%20of%20the%20opacity%20and%20uncertainty%26quot%3B%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20suppose%20the%20whole%20incident%20is%20a%20visible%20reminder%20of%20the%20arbitrariness%20of%20the%20PRC%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Chong%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20believe%20that%20the%20details%20surrounding%20Qin's%20removal%20could%20be%20revealed%20in%20due%20course.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20at%20some%20point%2C%20we%20will%20hear%20from%20Beijing.%20It%20is%20not%20good%20from%20Beijing's%20perspective%20for%20speculation%20and%20rumors%20to%20be%20flying%20so%20wildly%20over%20Qin's%20disappearance%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20his%20disappearance%2C%26quot%3B%20Dylan%20Loh%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20when%20and%20in%20what%20form%20this%20accounting%20will%20take%20place%20is%20entirely%20Beijing's%20prerogative%2C%26quot%3B%20Loh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EQin%20had%20been%20absent%20from%20the%20public%20eye%20for%20a%20month%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQin's%20removal%20comes%20after%20weeks%20of%20speculation%20following%20his%20disappearance%20in%20June.%20He%20was%20last%20seen%20publicly%20on%20June%2025%2C%20when%20he%20held%20meetings%20with%20diplomats%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cgtn.com%2Fnews%2F2023-06-25%2FChinese-FM-meets-Russian-deputy-FM-in-Beijing-1kVj1t5IkUg%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cgtn.com%2Fnews%2F2023-06-25%2FFMs-of-China-Vietnam-meet-in-Beijing-1kVCfT3thzq%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVietnam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cgtn.com%2Fnews%2F2023-06-25%2FChinese-Sri-Lankan-FMs-meet-in-Beijing-1kVkcBo5joI%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESri%20Lanka%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20Wenbin%2C%20a%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20briefing%20on%20July%2011%20that%20Qin%20was%20unable%20to%20attend%20a%20diplomatic%20gathering%20in%20Indonesia%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20health%20reasons.%26quot%3B%20Wang's%20remarks%20were%20widely%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fwang-yi-represent-china-asean-raising-questions-over-qin-gang-whereabouts-2023-07-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20international%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fchina-foreign-minister-ill-asean-9b69d1040c79062936e18d131410ba17%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutlets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20were%20conspicuously%20absent%20in%20the%20briefing's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fmfa_eng%2Fxwfw_665399%2