art%20of%20the%20DMRC%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Metro%20trains%20ferry%20commuters%20between%20Delhi%20and%20NCR%20cities%20like%20Noida%2C%20Ghaziabad%20(both%20in%20UP)%2C%20Gurgaon%20and%20Faridabad%20(in%20Haryana).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20excise%20department%20rules%20in%20Delhi%2C%20liquor%20cannot%20be%20sold%20to%20any%20person%20below%20the%20age%20of%2025%2C%20while%20in%20Haryana's%20Gurugram%2C%20it%20can%20be%20sold%20to%20anyone%20who%20is%20above%2018.%20In%20UP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20legal%20drinking%20age%20is%2021.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Metro%20trains%20ferry%20commuters%20between%20Delhi%20and%20NCR%20cities%20like%20Noida%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Gurgaon%20and%20Faridabad%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20Delhi's%20excise%20department%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Excise%20Act%20allows%20only%20one%20sealed%20bottle%20of%20liquor%20like%20rum%2C%20vodka%20and%20whisky%20to%20be%20carried%20from%20one%20state%20to%20another.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20one%20sealed%20bottle%20is%20allowed%20whereas%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20limit%20is%20one%20litre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMRC%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20on%20what%20items%20are%20permitted%20for%20carriage%20on%20Metro%20trains%20is%20based%20upon%20permissibility%20by%20the%20security%20agency%20in%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPassengers%20are%20expected%20to%20follow%20extant%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20concerned%20state%20excise%20department%20with%20regard%20to%20carrying%20liquor%20during%20cross-border%20transit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DMRC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bconcern%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20excise%20department%20will%20be%20conveyed%20to%20the%20security%20agency%20to%20examine%20accordingly%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-bottle%20norm%20was%20recommended%20by%20a%20committee%20comprising%20DMRC%20and%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20security%20at%20Metro%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690362960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Flcqg4qo8_delhi-metro-parting-ways-650_625x300_20_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fexplained-why-delhi-wants-metros-2-liquor-bottles-allowed-rule-changed-4241259%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22DMRC%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20on%20what%20items%20are%20permitted%20for%20carriage%20on%20Metro%20trains%20is%20based%20upon%20permissibility%20by%20the%20security%20agency%20in%20charge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fexplained-why-delhi-wants-metros-2-liquor-bottles-allowed-rule-changed-4241259%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fexplained-why-delhi-wants-metros-2-liquor-bottles-allowed-rule-changed-4241259%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fexplained-why-delhi-wants-metros-2-liquor-bottles-allowed-rule-changed-4241259%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Myanmar%20'categorically%20rejects'%20claims%20made%20by%20Sky%20News%20about%20the%20civil%20war%20in%20the%20country%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690362360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-myanmar-coup_6222235.jpg%3F20230718144116%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmyanmar-categorically-rejects-claims-made-by-sky-news-about-the-civil-war-in-the-country-12927705%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Myanmar%20has%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bcategorically%20rejects%26quot%3B%20claims%20made%20by%20Sky%20News%20in%20its%20undercover%20reporting%20of%20the%20civil%20war%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUr