20to%20designate%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20and%20other%20Pakistan-based%20operatives%20as%20international%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Doval%20mentioned%20that%20listing%20terrorists%20and%20their%20proxies%20under%20the%20UN%20counter-terrorism%20sanctions%20regime%20is%20an%20area%20in%20which%20BRICS%20can%20work%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20that%20the%20decision-making%20of%20the%20UNSC%20sanctions%20committee%20is%20free%20from%20politicisation%20and%20double%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20without%20naming%20any%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRICS%20bloc%20comprises%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%20and%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%2013th%20BRICS%20NSAs%20meeting%2C%20Doval%20said%20that%20terrorism%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20key%20threats%20to%20national%20peace%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTerror%20organisations%20in%20the%20Af-Pak%20region%20continue%20to%20operate%20with%20impunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Doval%20mentioned%20that%20the%20BRICS%20NSAs%20meeting%20was%20being%20held%20at%20a%20time%20of%20great%20churn%20in%20the%20international%20security%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20security%20situation%20is%20marked%20by%20uncertainty%20and%20rising%20tensions%20and%20the%20global%20economy%20is%20still%20recovering%20from%20the%20aftereffects%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Doval%20said%20the%20global%20commons%20of%20cyber%2C%20maritime%20and%20space%20are%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20non-traditional%20challenges%20of%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20energy%20security%20are%20witnessing%20stress%20and%20the%20inclusion%20of%20these%20topics%20by%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20BRICS%20NSA's%20Meeting%20reflects%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20the%20broader%20dimensions%20of%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appreciated%20the%20cooperation%20extended%20by%20South%20Africa%20for%20the%20ongoing%20G20%20Presidency%20of%20India%20and%20assured%20India's%20continued%20support%20for%20South%20Africa's%20BRICS%20chairship%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Doval%20pitched%20for%20the%20utilisation%20of%20regional%20mechanisms%20to%20advance%20common%20goals%20and%20address%20emerging%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20efforts%20need%20to%20be%20made%20to%20ensure%20equitable%20and%20fair%20access%20to%20global%20commons%20in%20line%20with%20international%20laws%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20water%20security%20is%20a%20major%20global%20issue%20and%20its%20prudent%20usage%20and%20conservation%20is%20a%20shared%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Doval%20mentioned%20instances%20of%20weaponisation%20of%20water%20and%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20complete%20transparency%20and%20unhindered%20information%20sharing%20with%20respect%20to%20shared%20cross-border%20water%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20politicisation%20of%20water%20needs%20to%20be%20countered%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20disputes%20with%20Pakistan%20on%20the%20sharing%20of%20river%20waters%20of%20the%20Indus%20River.%20India%20has%20also%20voiced%20concern%20over%20China's%20dam-building%20activities%20in%20Tibet%20on%20the%20Brahmaputra%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Doval%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20United%20Nations%20has%20declared%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20supporting%20educational%20and%20behavioural%20approaches%20through%20initiatives%20like%20Lifestyle%20for%20Environment%20(LiFE)%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20BRICS%20countries%20should%20set%20an%20example%20for%20the%20world%20by%20focusing%20on%20individual%20behaviour%20and%20making%20a%20shift%20to%20Lifestyle%20for%20Environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Doval%20said%20India%20was%20a%20major%20actor%20in%20the%20global%20food%20supply%20system%20and%20has%20assisted%20many%20countries%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20along%20with%20the%20supply%20of%20food%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20ensure%20unhindered%20availability%20of%20fertilisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Doval%20said%20today's%20fertiliser%20shortage%20could%20be%20tomorrow's%20food%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20importance%20of%20research%20and%20development%20occupies%20primacy%20in%20the%20cyber%20domain%20to%20confront%20common%20threats%20and%20risks%20due%20to%20emerging%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20satisfaction%20that%20the%20BRICS%20working%20group%20on%20ICTs%20has%20identified%20some%20cutting-edge%20areas%20like%20AI%2C%20quantum%20computing%2C%20cloud%20security%2C%20Blockchain%20and%20the%20Internet%20of%20Things%20as%20possible%20Research%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20mentioned%20that%20the%20opportunities%20presented%20by%20the%20digital%20age%20will%20also%20throw%20up%20challenges%20and%20the%20need%20to%20be%20united%20to%20fortify%20cyber%20defences%2C%20foster%20international%20cooperation%20and%20build%20a%20resilient%20national%20cyber%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20cyber%20attacks%20know%20no%20borders%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20linkage%20between%20cyber%20criminals%20and%20terrorists%20is%20an%20emerging%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Doval%20said%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20have%20had%20a%20disproportional%20effect%20on%20the%20food%20security%20of%20vulnerable%20populations.%20This%20needs%20to%20be%20urgently%20addressed%20which%20is%20a%20shared%20commitment%20and%20common%20responsibility%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20a%20secure%20and%20affordable%20supply%20of%20critical%20materials%20for%20the%20development%20of%20clean%20energy%20technologies%20is%20crucial%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20India's%20G20%20Presidency%2C%20one%20of%20the%20priorities%20is%20to%20voice%20the%20concerns%20of%20developing%20countries%2C%20Mr%20Doval%20said%2C%20adding%20India%20was%20proposing%20to%20create%20a%20global%20biofuel%20alliance%20under%20G-20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20the%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20summit%20hosted%20by%20India%20in%20which%20125%20countries%20participated%20and%20that%20this%20year%20the%20G20%20agenda%20under%20India's%20Presidency%20will%20truly%20encompass%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20world%2C%20especially%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20attached%20paramount%20importance%20to%20the%20BRICS%20process%20and%20is%20willing%20and%20prepared%20to%20enhance%20cooperation%20in%20all%20joint%20efforts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690361160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F6jk9l5lk_ajit-doval_625x300_29_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-dovals-double-standards-jab-over-terrorists-china-present-at-meet-4240602%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20China%2C%20NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%20said%20BRICS%20could%20work%20together%20on%20listing%20terrorists%20and%20their%20proxies%20under%20the%20UN%20counter-terror%20sanctions%20regime%20but%20emphasised%20the%20process%20should%20be%20free%20from%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20and%20double%20standards.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-dovals-double-standards-jab-over-terrorists-china-present-at-meet-4240602%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-dovals-double-standards-jab-over-terrorists-china-present-at-meet-4240602%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.