0learning%20are%20laid%20during%20these%20years.%20Getting%20the%20foundations%20right%20carries%20huge%20future%20benefits%3A%20better%20learning%20in%20school%20and%20higher%20educational%20attainment%2C%20which%20results%20in%20major%20social%20and%20economic%20gains%20for%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20820px)%20100vw%2C%20820px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22inclusive%20education%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%20820w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-500x282.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-768x433.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325144%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUNICEF%20reports%20that%20the%20early%20years%20are%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20period%20of%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20lifetime%3B%20Photo%3A%20Representational%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202020%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F234151%2Fnew-education-policy-2020-pdf-hrd-ministry-play-school-classes-vocational-coding-bagless-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Education%20Policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20laid%20great%20emphasis%20on%20inclusion%20in%20education%20