ps%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20focus%20is%20not%20to%20only%20earn%20an%20income%20from%20these%20guests%20but%20also%20to%20treat%20them%20nicely%20because%20they%20are%20our%20guests.%20They%20should%20be%20happy%20when%20they%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20even%20pay%20me%20extra%20on%20their%20own%20out%20of%20love.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20delectable%20meals%2C%20these%20tourists%20also%20enjoy%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20who%20does%20not%20miss%20a%20chance%20to%20entertain%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20apply%20henna%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20their%20palms%20and%20help%20our%20women%20guests%20wear%20a%20saree%20with%20bangles%20and%20bindi.%20I%20also%20apply%20%3Cem%3Esindoor%20%3C%2Fem%3E(vermillion)%20to%20them.%20They%20are%20enthusiastic%20to%20participate%20in%20all%20these%20activities%20and%20show%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20knowing%20the%20Indian%20culture.%20They%20often%20request%20me%20to%20narrate%20stories%20of%20gods%20and%20goddesses%2C%20explain%20the%20significance%20of%20%3Cem%3Etulsi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(basil)%20plant%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20celebrate%20their%20birthdays.%20In%20their%20own%20dialects%2C%20they%20lovingly%20call%20me%20%E2%80%98aunty%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Shashi%2C%20teaching%20these%20foreign%20tourists%20helps%20her%20feel%20empowered.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20believed%20in%20hard%20work.%20No%20one%20can%20defeat%20you%20if%20you%20believe%20in%20yourself.%20%3Cem%3ERoya%20daan%20nai%20milta%2C%20aur%20maangi%20bheek%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20won%E2%80%99t%20always%20get%20alms%20by%20crying).%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20have%20learnt%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20crying%20in%20front%20of%20others%2C%20empower%20yourself%20to%20go%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689946319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-3-1689859353.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D324582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20losing%20her%20husband%2C%20Shashikala%20Sanadhya%20took%20care%20of%20her%20family%20by%20starting%20Shashi%20Cooking%20Classes.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20taught%20over%201%2C000%20foreign%20tourists%20how%20to%20cook%20homely%20Indian%20food%20like%20chapati%2C%20naan%2C%20pakora%2C%20chutney%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A297%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324582%2Fshashikala-sanadhya-gives-indian-food-cooking-lessons-for-foreign-tourists-in-udaipur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Play%2C%20Learn%2C%20Grow%2C%20Repeat%3A%20A%20Peak%20Inside%20India%E2%80%99s%20Innovative%2C%20DIY%2C%20Sustainable%20Playgrounds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20published%20in%20collaboration%20with%20EkStep%20Foundation.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pooja%20Rai%20was%20a%20student%20of%20architecture%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F275217%2Fiit-kharagpur-innovation-oral-cancer-screening-cheap-device%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%2C%20Kharagpur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20would%20volunteer%20at%20Disha%20Seema%20Care%20Centre%2C%20a%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20located%20on%20campus.%20During%20one%20visit%2C%20she%20observed%20a%20few%20girls%20playing%20on%20broken%20cement%20pipes%20while%20some%20construction%20work%20was%20going%20on%20nearby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20extremely%20unsafe%20because%20you%20had%20wires%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20pipes%20and%20there%20were%20broken%20pieces%20of%20cement%20lying%20around.%20I%20also%20saw%20some%20boys%20at%20school%20trying%20to%20play%20a%20game%20of%20badminton%20with%20their%20slippers.%20Even%20though%20there%20was%20so%20much%20joy%20in%20that%20space%2C%20it%20just%20made%20me%20think%20that%20these%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20access%20to%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20a%20playground.%20Talking%20to%20my%20friend%20that%20evening%2C%20we%20discussed%20how%20we%20could%20use%20all%20the%20design%20knowledge%20that%20we%20learned%20to%20build%20a%20playground%20for%20these%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Pooja%20and%20her%20batchmates%20were%20students%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Instead%20of%20building%20a%20conventional%20playground%20with%20a%20jungle%20gym%2C%20merry%20go%20round%20and%20slides%2C%20they%20got%20innovative%2C%20brought%20a%20few%20tires%20together%2C%20and%20built%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201193px)%20100vw%2C%201193px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221193%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Playgrounds%20for%20children%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320.jpg%201193w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-300x183.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-500x306.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-768x469.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-150x92.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324513%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlayground%20at%20the%20Disha%20Seema%20Care%20Centre.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20%E2%80%98DIY%E2%80%99%20playground%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20struggled%20to%20collect%20tires%2C%20but%20we%20got%20lucky%20after%20reaching%20out%20to%20a%20few%20companies.%20Michelin%2C%20a%20global%20tyre%20manufacturer%2C%20sponsored%20the%20very%20first%20playground%20we%20built.%20They%20sent%20us%20used%20tires%2C%20with%20which%20we%20built%20swings%20and%20other%20play%20elements%20for%20children.%20They%20also%20sponsored%20a%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20funding%20came%20from%20our%20college%20alumni.%20We%20built%20our%20first%20playground%20in%202015%20and%20it%20was%20completely%20DIY%20(%E2%80%98do%20it%20yourself%E2%80%99)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Rai%20and%20her%20batchmates%20built%20here%20was%20a%20low-cost%20(barely%20Rs%2020%2C000)%20and%20sustainable%20playground%20for%20underprivileged%20children.%20According%20to%20Rai%2C%20mass%20produced%20recreational%20equipment%20for%20building%20a%20playground%20at%20the%20time%20would%20typically%20cost%20about%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20media%20coverage%20and%20inquiries%20from%20all%20around%20the%20country%20to%20build%20similar%20structures.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20January%202017%2C%20Rai%20and%20her%20friends%20quit%20their%20jobs%20full%20time%20and%20established%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20non-profit%20called%20Anthill%20Creations%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Ctransforms%20spaces%20into%20interactive%20and%20sustainable%20playgrounds%20by%20upcycling%20waste%20materials%20like%20tyres%2C%20oil%20and%20cable%20drums.%E2%80%9D%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20built%20around%20380%20low-cost%20and%20sustainable%20playgrounds%20for%20children%20across%2022%20states%20including%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Tripura%2C%20amongst%20others.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20are%20playgrounds%20important%20for%20children%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%20Educationists%20note%20that%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fchildhooddialogues%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20childhood%20care%20and%20education%20(ECCE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20play-based%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCZjg3gapFqJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCZjg3gapFqJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCZjg3gapFqJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Anthill%20Creations%20Foundation%20(%40anthillcreations)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20play-based%20learning%20matters%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20science%20and%20what%20we%20know%2C%20and%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%2C%20play%20is%20an%20important%20way%20for%20the%20child%20to%20learn.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20%E2%80%98playing%E2%80%99%20as%20we%20know%20it.%20It%20includes%20singing%20songs%2C%20conversations%2C%20stories%2C%20music%2C%20puzzles%2C%20dancing%2C%20etc.%20It%20is%20what%20the%20child%20does%20naturally%2C%20or%20as%20we%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98play%20is%20child%E2%80%99s%20work%E2%80%99.%20When%20a%20child%20is%20playing%2C%20they%20are%20learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shankar%20Maruwada%2C%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20of%20EkStep%20Foundation%20and%20member%2C%20National%20Steering%20Committee%20for%20the%20National%20Curriculum%20Frameworks%20(NCF)%2C%20in%20an%20earlier%20interaction%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20line%20of%20thinking%20has%20been%20emphasised%20by%20policymakers%20in%20India%20with%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%20and%20the%20National%20Curriculum%20Framework%20for%20School%20Education%20(NCF)%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(You%20can%20read%20more%20about%20play-based%20learning%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298277%2Fnep-early-childhood-care-and-education-play-based-learning-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304738%2Fnational-curriculum-framework-for-foundational-stage-education-children-india-ekstep%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20different%20modes%20of%20play%2C%20a%20playground%20presents%20one%20of%20the%20key%20platforms%20where%20a%20child%20can%20engage%20in%20play-based%20learning%20for%20cognitive%20and%20behavioural%20development.%20But%20nearly%20half%20of%20all%20public-funded%20schools%20in%20India%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20playgrounds%2C%20notes%20government%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fover-40-govt-schools-dont-have-power-playgrounds-parliamentary-panel%2Farticle61964470.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnified%20District%20Information%20System%20for%20Education%20(UDISE)%202017-18%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20less%20than%2057%25%20of%20schools%20have%20playgrounds.%20In%20states%20like%20Odisha%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20less%20than%2030%25%20of%20schools%20have%20playgrounds.%20Other%20surveys%20indicate%20that%20even%20major%20cities%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20playgrounds.%20Take%20Bengaluru%2C%20for%20example.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Janaagraha%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20think-tank%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20a%20population%20of%2012%20million%20(unofficial%20estimate%2C%208.4%20million%20as%20per%202011%20census)%20and%20an%20area%20of%20709%20sq.km%2C%20the%20city%20of%20Bengaluru%20has%20only%2019.31%20sq.km%20dedicated%20towards%20open%20spaces%20like%20parks%20and%20playgrounds.%20This%20translates%20to%202.2%20sq.m%20of%20open%20space%20per%20person%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20short%20of%20the%20recommended%2010-12%20sq.m%20by%20the%20URDPFI%20(Urban%20and%20Regional%20Development%20Plans%20Formulation%20and%20Implementation*)%20guidelines%20set%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Urban%20Development%20(MoUD)%2C%20India.%E2%80%9D%20What%E2%80%99s%20worse%2C%20only%2039%25%20of%20playgrounds%20in%20the%20city%20have%20playing%20equipment%20and%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrikanth%20Viswanathan%2C%20CEO%20at%20Janaagraha%20Centre%20for%20Citizenship%20and%20Democracy%2C%20notes%20that%20although%20the%20survey%20was%20taken%20in%202017%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthings%20haven%E2%80%99t%20changed%20much%20since%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20unfortunate%20reality%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Right%20of%20Children%20to%20Free%20and%20Compulsory%20Education%20Act%2C%202009%20(RTE)%20legislated%20by%20Parliament%20mandates%20that%20all%20school-going%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%206%20and%2014%20should%20be%20guaranteed%20access%20to%20playgrounds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20797px)%20100vw%2C%20797px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-1-1689854030.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22797%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Playgrounds%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-1-1689854030.jpg%20797w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-1-1689854030-300x288.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-1-1689854030-500x480.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-1-1689854030-768x737.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-1-1689854030-150x144.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324512%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22765%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAccessibility%20for%20all%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20build%20a%20playground%3F%20Speaking%20to%20The%20%3Cstrong%3EBetter%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rai%20begins%20with%20first%20principles.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20principle%20we%20follow%20is%20that%20where%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20playground%20and%20people%20cannot%20afford%20it%2C%20we%20are%20happy%20to%20build%20these%20structures%20in%20those%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20is%20that%20even%20if%20we%20build%20one%20or%20two%20playgrounds%20in%20the%20area%2C%20it%20motivates%20other%20people%20in%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20and%20creates%20awareness%20around%20the%20importance%20of%20play%20and%20how%20much%20good%20it%20can%20do.%20The%20playground%20is%20also%20usually%20shared%20by%20nearby%20communities%20or%20schools.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20one%20school%20where%20we%20built%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20far%2C%20Anthill%20Creations%20has%20built%20playgrounds%20in%20major%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20to%20the%20remote%20corners%20of%20states%20like%20Meghalaya%20and%20Tripura.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20an%20example%20of%20how%20they%20built%20playgrounds%20for%20four%20government%20schools%20in%20rural%20Meghalaya.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Abhishek%20Gowda%2C%20the%20sub-divisional%20officer%20(civil)%20of%20Dadenggre%20%5Bsubdivision%5D%20in%20West%20Garo%20Hills%20district%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20recalls%20the%20work%20Anthill%20did.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20January%202023%2C%20Anthill%20Creations%20approached%20me%20to%20facilitate%20the%20site%20selection%20process%20for%20these%20playgrounds%20under%20their%20project%20titled%20%E2%80%98Bring%20Back%20Play%20by%20Making%20it%20Accessible%20to%20All%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20Their%20team%20visited%20around%2010%20rural%20schools%20in%20my%20sub-division%2C%20and%20finalised%20on%20four%20where%20they%20would%20build%20playgrounds.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20March%2C%20the%20Anthill%20team%20began%20building%20these%20playgrounds%20using%20old%20rubber%20tires%20and%20other%20scrap%20material.%20You%20had%20see-saws%2C%20elephant-shaped%20play%20elements%20and%20swings%20made%20of%20scrap%20rubber%20tires%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gowda.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20constructing%20these%20playgrounds%2C%20the%20Anthill%20team%20conducted%20an%20extensive%20quality%20check%20process%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20structures%20are%20safe%20for%20children%20to%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20quality%20check%20was%20done%2C%20they%20handed%20over%20the%20playgrounds%20to%20their%20respective%20schools%20and%20communities.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C%20these%20playgrounds%20were%20built%20and%20ready%20to%20use.%20Today%2C%20children%20are%20actually%20utilising%20these%20playgrounds%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20enthusiasm%20and%20happiness.%20These%20playgrounds%20have%20also%20transformed%20the%20environment%20in%20these%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGowda%20and%20his%20administration%E2%80%99s%20task%20in%20building%20these%20playgrounds%20was%20simple.%20They%20provided%20any%20administrative%20and%20logistical%20support%20the%20Anthill%20team%20needed.%20Funding%20for%20this%20project%20came%20from%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%E2%80%99s%20CSR%20fund%20and%20all%20the%20work%20of%20actually%20selecting%20the%20sites%20and%20building%20these%20playgrounds%20was%20done%20by%20the%20Anthill%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20the%20main%20objective%20is%20to%20develop%20play-based%20learning%20infrastructure%20for%20early%20childhood%20development%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20improvements%20in%20school%20enrolment%20numbers%20and%20reduction%20in%20dropouts.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20these%20colourful%20playgrounds%2C%20the%20atmosphere%20in%20these%20schools%20feel%20a%20lot%20more%20welcoming%20to%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Gowda.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2080%25%20of%20the%20playgrounds%20Anthill%20has%20built%20are%20in%20government%20schools%2C%20but%20they%20also%20build%20them%20in%20public%20places.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20built%20a%20lot%20of%20public%20park%20playgrounds%20in%20Bengaluru%20like%20in%20Agara%20Lake%2C%20for%20example.%20We%20also%20partnered%20with%20another%20organisation%20called%20Recity%20to%20start%20building%20playgrounds%20in%20tourist%20hotspots%20Nainital%20and%20Darjeeling%20so%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20more%20awareness%20around%20recycling.%20Those%20are%20places%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20visit%2C%20so%20they%20generate%20a%20lot%20of%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20challenging%20for%20us%20to%20work%20in%20public%20spaces%20because%20you%E2%80%99d%20have%20to%20work%20with%20multiple%20authorities.%20It%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20get%20permission%20from%20all%20stakeholders%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchools%2C%20however%2C%20are%20where%20most%20children%20are%20present.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20typically%2C%20what%20I%20have%20seen%20in%20government%20schools%20is%20that%20they%20keep%20their%20playgrounds%20open%20to%20neighbouring%20children.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20really%20just%20the%20school%20children%20who%20are%20playing%20in%20those%20playgrounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201274px)%20100vw%2C%201274px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689860816.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221274%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Playgrounds%20for%20young%20boys%20and%20girls%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689860816.jpg%201274w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689860816-300x199.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689860816-500x331.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689860816-768x508.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playground-5-1689860816-150x99.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324637%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22843%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20elephants%20and%20horses%20to%20rockets%20on%20the%20playground%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rai%20and%20her%20colleagues%20started%20building%20playgrounds%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20build%20the%20typical%20elements%20that%20already%20exist%20like%20a%20jungle%20gym%2C%20see-saw%2C%20merry%20go%20round%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20correct%20way%20to%20go%20about%20any%20design%20is%20asking%20the%20user%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do.%20In%20the%20early%20days%2C%20we%20would%20talk%20to%20the%20children.%20Some%20of%20the%20very%20first%20designs%20that%20we%20developed%20were%20thanks%20to%20children.%20We%20used%20to%20go%20to%20these%20schools%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20conduct%20activities%20and%20play%20games%20with%20them.%20Children%20used%20to%20come%20up%20with%20amazing%20ideas.%20They%20would%20want%20a%20slide%20from%20their%20classroom%20to%20the%20playground%20or%20a%20water%20fountain%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20slide.%20We%20did%20not%20exactly%20translate%20what%20they%20said%20but%20we%20got%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20they%20wanted%20in%20a%20playground%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20play%20elements%20you%20see%20on%20playgrounds%20built%20by%20Anthill%20like%20octopus%2C%20elephants%20or%20horses%20came%20from%20children.%20Other%20children%20wanted%20a%20rocket%20in%20their%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20incorporate%20some%20of%20those%20major%20structural%20designs%2C%20but%20also%20keep%20activities%20in%20mind%20when%20we%20were%20designing%20those%20final%20elements.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20iterations.%20Not%20all%20of%20our%20design%20elements%20became%20successful%20in%20the%20first%20go%2C%20but%20we%20seek%20to%20ensure%20a%20constant%20feedback%20loop%20that%20happened.%20We%20still%20engage%20in%20these%20processes%2C%20but%20today%20we%20have%20around%20100%20different%20designs%20in%20our%20design%20library%20although%20we%20still%20take%20requests%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%E2%80%99re%20operating%20at%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%20today%2C%20we%20have%20this%20written%20site%20survey%20form%20that%20either%20we%20fill%20when%20we%20visit%20a%20site%20or%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20local%20community%20or%20a%20teacher%20who%20fills%20it%20out%20for%20us.%20That%20basically%20captures%20what%20children%20need%20and%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20in%20specific%20that%20like%20that%20particular%20community%20or%20school%20wants%20to%20do%2C%20we%20look%20at%20our%20design%20library%20and%20see%20what%20fits%20well%20into%20this%20playground.%20We%20try%20to%20leave%20some%20space%20for%20designing%20new%20elements%20as%20well%20because%20we%20want%20to%20give%20some%20unique%20touch%20to%20most%20of%20our%20playgrounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20756px)%20100vw%2C%20756px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22756%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Innovative%20playgrounds%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074.jpg%20756w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074-281x300.jpg%20281w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074-500x534.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-1689861074-150x160.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22807%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPretend%20Play%20Element%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20an%20elephant.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20they%20make%20these%20playgrounds%20inclusive%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20stated%20earlier%2C%20there%20are%20playgrounds%20with%20elements%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20from%20their%20design%20library.%20After%20all%2C%20they%20have%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20children%2C%20including%20those%20living%20with%20disabilities.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20they%20built%20a%20playground%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Sankalp%20Learning%20Centre%20in%20Chennai%20for%20children%20with%20auti